{
  "stem": "11184.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And sure enough, a second later, the doors open like a-- like-- like an-- ugh-- with such a bang-- and the screams, and the yells.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[GERMAN]!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Out, out, out!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you couldn't even concentrate where you are and what's going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "By the time I knew, I was walking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what happened, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You just couldn't-- couldn't understand what's going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We walked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was lucky at this-- this time too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and we came in to this place where they were shaving us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were, you know, bathing, us, and giving you, you know, like one-- one person got the top of a pajama, the other person got the bottom of the pajama.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, and this took till late at night when it was dark.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we came in, and-- and then they let us go out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't know where I'm going and what we are doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody's crying.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody recognizes anybody anymore, because all the hair is gone, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people change.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They see environments like that, they-- you-- so a sister couldn't recognize a sister.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they brought us into one place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I touched, and I touched, and I touched.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where are we?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I found a hole.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I touched again, and there's another hole.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So later on I learned this was the bathroom for 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had this bathroom, the holes, for so many people to come in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there they kept us for a little while until they brought us in to the barracks there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So there was a-- a girl, you know, she was a neighbor of mine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I knew her.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
